<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_320px] gap-8 relative">
  <div class="bg-white/95 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 space-y-10 text-center">
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-rose-400">Proverb Maker</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">ことわざを仕上げよう</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">送られてきた 2 つの言葉から、タイトル・意味・用例を紡いでください。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] gap-6 items-center">
      <% [[@proverb.word1, "Word 1"], [@proverb.word2, "Word 2"]].each_with_index do |(word, label), index| %>
        <div class="relative group space-y-2">
          <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400"><%= label %></label>
          <div class="w-full py-3 px-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 text-center font-semibold select-none">
            <%= word.presence || "まだありません" %>
          </div>
          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/70 text-white text-sm font-medium opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">
            相手が入力します
          </div>
        </div>
        <% if index.zero? %>
          <span class="text-3xl font-black text-rose-400 select-none text-center">✕</span>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-left">
      <div>
        <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">タイトル</label>
        <%= f.text_field :title,
              placeholder: "ないないことわざ",
              class: "w-full py-3 px-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white text-center text-lg font-semibold shadow-sm focus:border-rose-400 focus:ring-rose-200" %>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">意味</label>
        <%= f.text_area :meaning,
              rows: 3,
              placeholder: "意味",
              class: "w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white text-base leading-relaxed shadow-sm focus:border-rose-400 focus:ring-rose-200" %>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400">用例</label>
        <%= f.text_area :example,
              rows: 4,
              placeholder: "用例",
              class: "w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white text-base leading-relaxed shadow-sm focus:border-rose-400 focus:ring-rose-200" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-2 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
      <%= f.hidden_field :status, value: "completed" %>
      <%= f.submit "投稿",
            class: "w-full sm:w-56 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <aside class="bg-white/95 rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-6 space-y-4 self-start" data-controller="accordion">
    <div class="text-center space-y-2">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600">一緒に作っているユーザー</p>
      <div class="border rounded-full px-5 py-1 inline-block bg-slate-50 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 shadow-sm">
        <%= @room.invitation.inviter.name %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button type ="button"
            data-action="click->accordion#toggle"
            class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-2xl py-2 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-slate-800 transition">
      使い方をみる
    </button>

    <div data-accordion-target="content"
         class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300"
         hidden>
      <p><strong>Step1.</strong> 相手が送った 2 つの言葉を確認します。</p>
      <p><strong>Step2.</strong> タイトル・意味・用例を入力します。</p>
      <p><strong>Step3.</strong> 投稿ボタンで完成。ことわざが公開されます。</p>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
